@node "DESCRIPTION" "Amiga Webcam Software (Description)"

                       @{b}D E S C R I P T I O N@{ub}

 
 @{b}@{i}Features:@{ui}@{ub}
 With this program you can use your digital camera as a webcam.
 A cool feature: when you go offline the programm sends a offline picture.
 You can replace this offline picture with your own picture.
 The picture must be 160x120 and in jpg format.


 
 @{b}@{i}Requirements:@{ui}@{ub}
 A Amiga computer with OS3.x and a TCP/IP stack.
 A serial digital camera supported by @{"Digicam" LINK "digicam"}.

 This program uses Digicam by Volker Remuß and PutClient by Ray Ake.
 Both programs are included in the AWS archive.



 @{b}@{i}Disclaimer:@{ui}@{ub}
